<seg id=1> Irish Republican Army announces ceases fire </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> New China News Agency London on August 31st electricity (reporter Li article is vast) Irish Republican Army today announces, this organization will thoroughly stops all military activity from today middle of the night, implementation " unconditionally and not by a set time " cease-fire. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=3> Irish Republican Army in announcement which disseminates publication to England and Ireland news says in one, considers current situation and in order to advances Northern Ireland peace advancement, this organization made above decision, and informed this one decision its subordinate's all army. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=4> Announcement requests responsibility which England government faces up to oneself undertakes, will urge concerned each side by to be firm and patience facing new situation which will bring by this time cease-fire, will hold by England and Ireland government as well as Northern Ireland each main political party participation widespread negotiations, finally will solve Northern Ireland's conflict. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=5> Announcement says, Irish Republican Army announces cease-fire, for Northern Ireland question " was fair and permanent solution " provides opportunity. </seg>
<seg id=6> But Irish Republican Army also reiterates, it still will abide by it " republican goal ", namely Ireland all island unification. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=7> For realizes Northern Ireland and Republic of Ireland's unification, Irish Republican Army had carried on in Northern Ireland long reaches 25 years violence activity. </seg>
</p> 
